        Parameters:
        edgeDetectorForBlackValueCalculation - an edge detector for the calculation of the inner areas of the circle-candidates
        edgeDetectorForCrossValueCalculation - an edge detector for the calculation of the crosses of the circles
        contrastEnhancerList - a list of contrast-enhancer which are all used to generate sharper edges for various images
        verbose - a boolean which determines if the calculated images should be shown
        referenceCircles - a list of reference-circles which are searched in the given image
